name: Wall Paneling - Ceccotti Collezioni
description: Wall paneling in American walnut without frame or with one or two frames. A design idea based on versatility and eclecticism. Work is a modular storage system made of solid American walnut and veneered plywood, a product which has changed over the years to meet different living needs. The choice of materials for the top, rather than the doors, allows the satisfaction of different aesthetic tastes. The base module has given rise to sideboards, dressers, top units, display cabinets, bookcases, wardrobes, TV cabinets and boiserie.
